reviewText: Extremely happy with everything. Thank you.
This DVD set is par excellence, and far better than "single" Washington discs offered in other similar series.

Foremost, these have been recorded in HD digital, so the resolution is astounding compared to older ones recorded with analog cameras.  It has alot of fly overs that feels like a ride.  It does have a few still views of cities and such, but it is probably the best one I have seen about Washington with Alaska DVD as a bonus.
